</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_249" id="124r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_249_r1l7"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Schellemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_249_r1l8">cʒu wageck</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_249_r1l9">Lieber her <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> / Vns hat fürgelegt Peter flexdorffer <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_249_r1l10">von <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> flexdorffers ſeins vater wegen / vvie daʒ Jr Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_249_r1l11">
<del rend="strikethrough">ij la </del> cʒwu laden mit kemmen aufgehalten vnd auff hohentann </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_249_r1l12">gefürt habt / vnd maint daʒ die auſʒlewte ſeın ſüllen / Nu hat der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_249_r1l13"><expan>eg<ex>enante</ex>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan></del>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> Peter flexdorffer die <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> cʒwu laden mit kemmen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_249_r1l14">vor vns cʒu den heẏligen behabt / daʒ dıe ſein vnd des <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ſeins </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_249_r1l15">vaters vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> ſein / Alſo / daʒ khein auſʒman vveder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_249_r1l16">teil noch gemein daran hab / <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſere<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> burge </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_249_r1l17"><expan>burger<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jr hab <expan>vvidergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / Auch als vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_249_r1l18"><expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> vormals von des fricʒen Meyers <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> vvegen 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_249_r1l20">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_249_r1l19"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haben </ab></add> als Er drew veſʒleın in <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> pellein mit <expan>grüne<ex>m</ex></expan> Jngeber </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_249_r1l21">vor vns auch cʒu den heẏligen behabt hat / Alſo hat vns derſelb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_249_r1l22"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> aber fürgelegt vvie Jm <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> drew veſʒlein mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_249_r1l23">Jngeber noch niht wider vvorden ſein / <expan>Bite<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir ewr erberkeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_249_r1l24"><expan>fleiſſıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr Jm <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein hab auch wider <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd on </ab>
